content.code: from PIL import Image, ImageFont, ImageDraw

im = Image.open("grid.png")
helvetica = ImageFont.truetype(filename="Helvetica.ttf", size=40)
d = ImageDraw.Draw(im)

location = (100, 50)
text_color = (100, 100, 200)
d.text(location, "Kite", font=helvetica, fill=text_color)

im.save("drawn_grid.png")
